Algorithm:
Text-Based Question Answering
1)Start
2)Store the input text as a string
3)Store predefined question templates
4)Accept a question from the user
5)Compare the question with stored templates
6)If a match is found:
7)Generate corresponding text pattern
8)Apply the text pattern to the input text
9)Extract the longest matching phrase
10)Display the extracted phrase as the answer
11)If no match is found, display “No answer found”
12)Stop

Flowchart:
 ┌───────────┐
 │   Start   │
 └─────┬─────┘
       │
 ┌─────▼─────┐
